{"tid":1431638,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣反送中] 有冇人想整個<反駁藍絲謬論大合成>","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T07:08:29.000Z","uid":181974,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0e8e3ce150e2236637b26f28b7b7a4b6be6ea6","tid":1431638,"uid":181974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:49:15.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人整個相關平台？<br />\n<br />\n[廣集各路巴絲] <br />\n<br />\n面對着不斷講謬論嘅藍絲父母親朋戚友，我地<strong>每日花好多時間逐一反駁唔係唔得，但係覺得有啲嘥時間嘥氣嘥心機</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n橫掂啲藍絲啲msg都係forward 再fwd 再fwd，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不如有心既ching 製造完一次駁斥嘅論點論據，再一次過響連登 (或者大合集 website) share 比其他巴絲。</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，引用第三者說話亦都有啲好處，可以為對話降降溫。<br />\nE.g. 1  有啲法律學者話, .... , <span style=\"color: red;\">你點睇？</span><br />\nE.g. 2  網上有人話, ....,<span style=\"color: red;\"> 佢有冇邊度講錯咗？</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思淨係拋橋，冇實際功勞。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力"},{"pid":"a3274e8d0415f9bb4b743abe7dc94cf175a08f49","tid":1431638,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:51:55.000Z","msg":"你提供藍絲 / 政府嘅論述，我嘗試反駁。<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dxBanT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dxBanT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"58ddac4500946aefdc95113c330f16c6c71006b5","tid":1431638,"uid":39752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:05:48.000Z","msg":"你可以睇吓徐緣嗰篇十八種藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無大台人人自己做文宣系列</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 人人都可以學做文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1430317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1430317</a><br />\n揀追故模式有多篇實用教學<br />\n<br />\n［新文宣方向］長輩圖vol2.0 深入中老年階層爭取支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1427547\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1427547</a><br />\n一齊參考老土長輩 slideshow<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/